    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/9305dc9fdb330f7fe91a0e0f7a56d2e3.poster.avif?t=1761033309\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/9305dc9fdb330f7fe91a0e0f7a56d2e3.webm?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/9305dc9fdb330f7fe91a0e0f7a56d2e3.mp4?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到Kleks Academy——在这个充满魔力的平台冒险世界中，你的创造力将重塑周遭万物！通过手绘创意解决谜题：搭建桥梁、勾勒阶梯，或发明全新方式突破障碍。在这里，想象力不仅是锦上添花——而是通关必备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放你内心的发明家潜能，潜入童话秘境，探寻无数秘密、惊喜与奇趣魅力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创意即力量</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用画笔在游戏世界中创造真实物件。探索涂鸦配方，掌握组合技巧，在每一关卡开辟专属路径——每个挑战都拥有多重解法，你的选择决定一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/3fd063a430f9aafcca89a976e96ea082.poster.avif?t=1761033309\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/3fd063a430f9aafcca89a976e96ea082.webm?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/3fd063a430f9aafcca89a976e96ea082.mp4?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探秘奇幻世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从魔法森林到学院隐秘角落，每处场景皆暗藏玄机。无压力自由探索，发现本身就是乐趣。伴随角色成长，解锁与魔法世界互动的新方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/380df37059f897ed70abc1a5946b8336.poster.avif?t=1761033309\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/380df37059f897ed70abc1a5946b8336.webm?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/380df37059f897ed70abc1a5946b8336.mp4?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>童话美学盛宴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅古灵精怪的角色，开启神秘任务，定制专属英雄体验独特冒险。探索受《天方夜谭》等传世经典启发的魔法篇章。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/b17b6608474abbb2dc86fadb049fadf8.poster.avif?t=1761033309\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/b17b6608474abbb2dc86fadb049fadf8.webm?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179870/extras/b17b6608474abbb2dc86fadb049fadf8.mp4?t=1761033309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
